Description: This is the research compendium \insertCite{Marwick.2019}{herdersmovementpatterns} for the
  manuscript "Patterns in Mongolian Nomadic Household Movement Derived from GPS Trajectories", including the
  Rmarkdown script, and data used to generate the manuscript. No raw trajectory data ar provided for ethical
  reasons.
